  "rationale": "Designed using Finsweet 6-layer logic. Layout is an asymmetrical CSS Grid (2fr 1fr) with a 2rem gap, mapping to the 843px left / 405px right visual ratio. Left card is explicitly 37.5rem height; right column is a nested grid with two rows of 17.75rem, aligning perfectly with the total 37.5rem height. As per MAS-V2-007, exact dimensions are mapped as 100% width and fixed rem height with object-fit: cover on placeholder images. Class names follow strictly Component_Element (e.g. our-work_component, our-work_overlay) with is- combo classes where needed."
